nodes.title: Partner Central
nodes.description: The Partner Central home page presents a collection of headline banners and sections that highlight the latest partner‑focused news, product announcements, and program updates from Cisco, Pure Storage, and Nutanix. Its primary purpose is to give resellers a quick overview of current marketing insights, new product availability, and upcoming partner initiatives so they can stay informed and act on the most recent opportunities. Visible features include rotating hero messages, thematic call‑outs such as “Stronger Together” and “Driving the Hybrid Revolution,” and links to deeper content about marketing insights, product releases, and the FY26 Elevate Partner Program.

nodes.title: Partner Central
nodes.description: The page is a “Sales Data – Bookings” view within Partner Central that lists individual booking opportunities in a tabular format. Its primary function is to let a reseller see the details of each opportunity—such as name, ID, customer, segment, type, stage, forecast category, products, and the associated reseller and distributor—so they can review and manage their sales pipeline. The key visible sections are the page header with navigation controls (including “View As”) and the comprehensive table that organizes all opportunity attributes for quick reference.

nodes.title: Partner Central
nodes.description: The page is a “Renewals Data” view within Partner Central that lists booking information in a table format, showing each renewal opportunity as a separate row. Its primary function is to let a reseller review and manage renewal bookings, with navigation elements such as the “View As” selector and the overall Partner Central header. The main visible sections are the page header (including the Nutanix copyright and navigation) and the data table, which currently indicates that no opportunities are present.
